<p>Great fun today with Dave, Greg, and Matt.  We fought the cuckoo-inducing Chinooks valiantly.  At least on Flagstaff, the wind is at your back in one direction of the hairpin turns!</p>
<p>My throat is utterly parched from our favorite little zephyr, though.  I drank an entire bottle of water to no avail.  Maybe I'll tote bottled oxygen next time.</p>
<p>If we do get some snow this weekend, get ready for duathlons next week&mdash;perhaps even "True Initiation".</p>